The pair invite random members of the public to make music with them . 
 They find an impressive singer and record a song with his vocals . 
 Brisbane DJ-duo Mashed N Kutcher uploaded the video last week . 
 It has had 1.25 million views and been covered by media around the globe . 
 The pair wanted to show that musical talent can be found anywhere . 
 The jogger in the clip, Ross Burbury, is a singer songwriter from Brisbane who works in direct sales for media company News Corporation . 
 